article_title: Ohio Gov. John Kasich Falsely Claims He 'Sued The Administration' Over ObamaCare (Part 3)

article_metadata.description: He could have joined the ObamaCare challenge. He didn’t. He could have made it a priority of his new administration. He didn’t. He was too busy trying to implement parts of ObamaCare he was under no obligation to implement.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
